#: src/rust-2018/macros/at-most-once.md:7
msgid ""
"In Rust 2018, we have made a couple of changes to the macros-by-example "
"syntax."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/macros/at-most-once.md:9
msgid ""
"We have added a new Kleene operator `?` which means \"at most one\" "
"repetition. This operator does not accept a separator token."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/macros/at-most-once.md:11
msgid ""
"We have disallowed using `?` as a separator to remove ambiguity with `?`."
msgstr ""

